Habits/Tasks : {

    A user cannot see or modify other users’ tasks/habits.
    
    A task cannot have a past due date when created (optional validation).
    
    A habit can only be marked once per day.
    
    Streaks increase if a habit is done consecutively; reset if skipped.
   
    };
    
Visual: {

    Login/Register → Users access the system.
    
    Task List → See all tasks, filter by category/priority.
    
    Habit Tracker → See today’s habits, mark done.
    
    Dashboard → Visualize stats.
    
    Profile/Settings → Change password, email, etc.
    
    };